This is project only contains the backend and the connection with the DB
************************************************************************
                THINGS LEARNED IN THIS PROJECT
************************************************************************

-> How to signup in Mongo DB and create a cluster
-> How to set user ID and Password
-> How to allow access of the DB from any network
-> How to download MongoDB Atlas and connect it with the online MongoDB cluster we created
-> How to do CRUD operation in the DB manually
-> How to connect the DB from express using the mongoose library
-> How to define the schema and how we can perform CRUD operation using the Models
-> How to perform above CRUD operation using the API like app.get('/signup', function(req,res){})
